Get an up-close look at what the skaters will be working with at this Saturday’s Tour Qualifier!

Tune in live on July 31st on our YouTube to see which 3 skaters earn a spot on the 2021 Championship Tour! Prelims at 1:30pm PT, Finals at 5:30pm PT  🖥
